OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for ramming cars
OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FA judge said it was a "miracle" that
OL,7,Fno-one was killed after a drunk driver
OL,8,Fwent on a 20 mile motorway rampage.
OL,10,FJames Loveridge, 28, rammed into other
OL,11,Fcars and drove the wrong way down the
OL,12,FM56 before eventually crashing into a
OL,13,Ffence in Wythenshawe, Manchester.
OL,15,FHis shocking driving terrorised other
OL,16,Fmotorists, with one, a veteran who had
OL,17,Fserved in Afghanistan, describing it
OL,18,Fas "one of the scariest incidents" he
OL,19,Fhad ever experienced.
