OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for ramming cars
OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FLoveridge, who was found to be two-and-
OL,7,Fa-half times over the drink drive
OL,8,Flimit, was jailed for just under two
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FProsecutors told how Loveridge was
OL,12,Fdriving on the M56 on Monday, March 4,
OL,13,Fwhen traffic was "heavy".
OL,15,FThe driver of an AA recovery truck
OL,16,Fbecame aware of Loveridge near
OL,17,Fjunction 12. Loveridge overtook the
OL,18,Ftruck and moved in front of it. He
OL,19,Fthen suddenly began to slam his
OL,20,Fbrakes, nearly causing the truck
OL,21,Fdriver to collide with it.
