OL,6,FHe said Loveridge continued in this
OL,7,Fmanner for about 10 minutes up to
OL,8,Fjunction ten, preventing the truck
OL,9,Fdriver from driving at more than
OL,10,F15mph. The truck driver took the
OL,11,Fopportunity to come off the motorway
OL,12,Fand call the police.
