OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for ramming cars
OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FHe was previously diagnosed with PTSD
OL,7,Fhaving served in Afghanistan, and he
OL,8,Fsuffered a panic attack in the
OL,9,Faftermath of the incident and said: "I
OL,10,Fhave served in Afghanistan and have
OL,11,Fbeen in situations that someone of
OL,12,Freasonable firmness cannot even
OL,13,Fimagine, however this was one of the
OL,14,Fscariest incidents I have ever been
OL,15,Finvolved in."
OL,17,FLoveridge continued along the motorway
OL,18,Fand another motorist spotted him
OL,19,F'drifting' into another lane. At first
OL,20,Fhe thought the driver may have fallen
OL,21,Fasleep, prosecutor Duncan Wilcock said.
