OL,6,FLoveridge hit the car causing damage
OL,7,Fto the mirror and door, and the other
OL,8,Fdriver stopped on the hard shoulder.
OL,9,FHe thought Loveridge was also going to
OL,10,Fstop, but he carried on.A taxi driver
OL,11,Fthen became the latest motorist to be
OL,12,Ftargeted by Loveridge.
