OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for ramming cars
OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FHe had seen the previous incident and
OL,7,Ftried to avoid Loveridge, but at one
OL,8,Fpoint the defendant gesticulated at
OL,9,Fhim and mouthed the words "I will kill
OL,10,Fyou" at him. The taxi driver slowed
OL,11,Fdown in the hope that Loveridge would
OL,12,Fdrive off, but he also reduced his
OL,13,Fspeed. Loveridge hit the taxi on three
OL,14,Fseparate occasions.
OL,16,FThe taxi pulled over onto the hard
OL,17,Fshoulder but Loveridge carried on,
OL,18,Fhaving reached junction six and then
OL,19,Fstarted to ram another car from behind.
