OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FShocked motorists had called the
OL,7,Fpolice, and a traffic officer tried to
OL,8,Fstop Loveridge. Instead Loveridge got
OL,9,Fpast and began to drive on the wrong
OL,10,Fside of the road from junction five,
OL,11,Ftravelling on the hard shoulder,
OL,12,Fbefore turning off at junction four at
OL,13,FWythenshawe.
