OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FLoveridge then drove along Simonsway,
OL,7,Fclipped a minibus and missed the
OL,8,Fturning before crashing into a fence.
OL,9,FHe stopped the car and ran off, but
OL,10,Fpolice caught him close-by.JHe was
OL,11,Ffound to be two-and-a-half times over
OL,12,Fthe drink drive limit in an initial
OL,13,Fbreath test, but later refused to
OL,14,Fcomply with a blood sample.
OL,16,FThe whole incident covered about 20
OL,17,Fmiles. Loveridge, of Firbank in Elton,
OL,18,FChester, pleaded guilty to dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving, failing to provide a specimen
OL,20,Fand driving without insurance. The van
OL,21,Fhe was driving was not his.
