OL,6,F"This incident of dangerous driving is
OL,7,Fone of the worst that I have seen over
OL,8,Fmany years as a crown court judge,"
OL,9,FJudge Suzanne Goddard KC told him.
OL,11,FShe continued: "One is more used to
OL,12,Fseeing such driving on TV dramas. It's
OL,13,Fa miracle nobody was hurt or killed
OL,14,Fthat day as a result of your driving."
