OL,6,FDefending, Daniel Bramhall said
OL,7,FLoveridge's strongest point in
OL,8,Fmitigation was his guilty pleas. He
OL,9,Fsaid that Loveridge has used the abuse
OL,10,Fof alcohol and drugs following the
OL,11,Fdeath of father when he was aged 15 as
OL,12,Fa "coping mechanism".
OL,14,FMr Bramhall said Loveridge is
OL,15,Fremorseful and "couldn't believe that
OL,16,Fthat was him in the footage".
