OL,4,Con motorway in 20 mile rampage
OL,6,FLoveridge was jailed for 21 months,
OL,7,Fand had an extra six weeks added to
OL,8,Fhis sentence after admitting being in
OL,9,Fbreach of a previous suspended
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,FHe was also banned from driving for
OL,13,Falmost four years, and must take an
OL,14,Fextended re-test before he can get
OL,15,Fbehind the wheel again.
